---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure" description="VPNVerdict affiliate disclosure. How we earn revenue and maintain editorial independence.">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="legal-page">
      <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <section>
        <h2>How We Earn Revenue</h2>
        <p>VPNVerdict is a participant in affiliate programs with NordVPN, ExpressVPN, Surfshark, CyberGhost, ProtonVPN, and other VPN providers. When you click our affiliate links and purchase a subscription, we earn a commission at no additional cost to you.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Editorial Independence</h2>
        <p>Affiliate commissions never influence our reviews, ratings, or recommendations. Our editorial team tests and evaluates every VPN independently. We include both pros and cons in every review, and our top picks are based on testing results, not affiliate payouts.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>How to Identify Affiliate Links</h2>
        <p>Links to VPN providers on our site (such as "Visit NordVPN" buttons and in-article links) are affiliate links. When you click these links, a cookie tracks the referral so we receive credit if you purchase.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Our Testing Process</h2>
        <p>Every VPN we review undergoes speed testing across multiple servers, security and leak testing, streaming platform checks, and usability evaluation on all major platforms. We re-test annually to keep our reviews current.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Questions?</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about our affiliate relationships or testing methodology, email us at <a href="mailto:info@vpnverdict.net">info@vpnverdict.net</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 0; }
  .legal-page h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .updated { color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .legal-page section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .legal-page h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: #10b981; }
  .legal-page p { color: #d1d8e0; line-height: 1.8; }
</style>
